s:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/09\/15\/pilgrims-guests-of-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":23706,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Pilgrims are special guests of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 15, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe pilgrims of Hajj and Umrah are the guests of Allah. He called them, and they answered him. They ask from Him, and He gives them.\u201d Source: Kashf al-Asta\u0304r 1075 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33132,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/09\/allah-boasts-pilgrims-arafah\/","url_meta":{"origin":23706,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Allah boasts of the pilgrims at Arafat","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty boasts to His angels of the pilgrims on the afternoon of the day of Arafat, saying: Look at My servants, coming to Me disheveled and dusty!\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 7089 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31143,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/25\/kab-mujahideen-pilgrims-guests\/","url_meta":{"origin":23706,"position":2},"title":"Ka\u2019b on Pilgrims: Soldiers and pilgrims are guest of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 25, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Damrah reported: Ka\u2019b, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThe pilgrims of Hajj and Umrah and soldiers in the way of Allah are the guests of Allah. If they ask, give them. If they call you, answer them.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 15463 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40536,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/03\/women-hajj-menstruation\/","url_meta":{"origin":23706,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Menses: Women performing Hajj will menstruating","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, enter my dwelling at Sarif while I was crying. The Prophet said, \u201cWhat is the matter? Are you menstruating?\u201d I said yes. The Prophet said, \u201cThis is a matter that Allah has decreed for the daughters of Adam,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38371,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/10\/24\/hajj-purifies-sin\/","url_meta":{"origin":23706,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Pilgrimage purifies from sins and poverty","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 24, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPerform the Hajj and \u2018Umrah pilgrimages, one after another, for they both erase poverty and sins just as the furnace removes impurity from iron, gold, and silver. There is no reward for an accepted Hajj\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3042,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/24\/pilgrims-makkah-madinah-quds\/","url_meta":{"origin":23706,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Pilgrimage: No religious travel but to Mecca, Medina, Jerusalem","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not undertake a religious journey but to three mosques: the Sacred Mosque in Mecca, the Mosque of the Messenger of Allah, and the Furthest Mosque in Jerusalem.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1189, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1397 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/23706","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.ab